Andrej Borsenkow wrote:

> (How) is it possible to specify mutually exclusive options in one line, like
> (-b --binary)?

You mean `if they mean/do the same thing'?

Something like:

  '(-b --binary)'-{b,-binary}'[...]:...'

should be enough.


